'''Buɣni''', ('''Boghni''' s [[taṛumit|tṛumit]], s [[tifinaɣ]] [[Image:2D31.png|13px|]][[Image:2D53.png|13px|]][[Image:2D56.png|13px|]][[Image:2D4F.png|13px|]][[Image:2D49.png|13px|]]), d [[taɣiwant n Tmurt Taqbaylit|taɣiwant]] n [[tawilayt n Tizi Uzzu]], di [[Tamurt Taqbaylit|Tmurt Taqbaylit]], tella ar azal n {{Aferdis|38|km}} deg unẓul-amalu n [[Tizi Uzzu]], ar {{Aferdis|15|km}} deg umalu n [[Iwaḍiyen]] dɣa ar {{Aferdis|13|km}} deg ugmuḍ n [[Draɛ Lmizan]].


== Amezruy ==
{{...}}
'''Tihawt taṭerkit'''
1515-1830
Agadir aqbur aṭerki. Ar 6 km n tiẓgi n Tineglin.
Isem azwaran :Burǧ-Buɣni

'''Tihawt taṛumit'''
1830 - 1962 
Taddart tamecṭuḥt n Tamurt Taqbaylit yettwaẓẓun deg waḍar n Ǧerǧer, taɣiwant tamasayt n Draɛ Lmizan tettweleq deg useggwas 1876 deg ugezdu n Zzayer asun n Palestru.
Tuɣaled d taɣiwant n alaɣmu acuṛan, attili tettweqqen deg useggwas 1958 ar ugezdu amaynu n Tizi Uzzu

